                                <path d="M25 10L0.999999 10" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" />
                            </svg></div>
                    </a></li>
                <li><a href="http://www.compex.cz/files/doplnky/Registry/FIS3000_Instalace_FoxFix.exe">
                        <div class="text-icon">Instalace FoxFix5.dll pro OS WinServer XX (chyba při kontrole
                            integrity)<svg width="28" height="20" viewBox="0 0 28 20" fill="none"
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <path d="M17 1L26 10L17 19" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" />
                                <path d="M25 10L0.999999 10" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" />
                            </svg></div>
                    </a></li>
                <li><a href="http://www.compex.cz/files/doplnky/Registry/2091_server_oplocks.reg">
